00:23:12,498 --> 00:23:15,018
so that he doesn't feel stifled
while staying in this temple.

560
00:23:15,817 --> 00:23:16,577
Your Majesty,

561
00:23:16,978 --> 00:23:19,458
I just talked with His Highness.

562
00:23:19,458 --> 00:23:21,418
It was indeed a pleasure to meet him.

563
00:23:22,418 --> 00:23:23,577
What did you talk about?

564
00:23:24,018 --> 00:23:24,817
I saw that His Highness

565
00:23:24,857 --> 00:23:26,617
was bored in Yuanyang Temple.

566
00:23:26,617 --> 00:23:28,698
So I offered to take him out
for a tour to open his eyes.

567
00:23:38,297 --> 00:23:40,018
I'm a bit tired today.

568
00:23:40,377 --> 00:23:41,857
We'll chat another day, Lord Ling.

569
00:23:42,658 --> 00:23:44,258
Yes, Your Majesty.

570
00:23:50,178 --> 00:23:51,057
Grandmother.

571
00:23:51,057 --> 00:23:52,224
(Believe in Buddhism)

572
00:23:52,377 --> 00:23:53,418
I want to go.

573
00:24:02,658 --> 00:24:03,297
Young Lord.

574
00:24:04,377 --> 00:24:04,978
Lord Ling.

575
00:24:06,377 --> 00:24:07,097
I will leave now.

576
00:24:07,097 --> 00:24:07,738
Alright.

577
00:24:27,658 --> 00:24:28,377
Father.

578
00:24:29,498 --> 00:24:30,218
You!

579
00:24:30,898 --> 00:24:32,057
Young Lord! Young Lord!

580
00:24:32,218 --> 00:24:34,018
Open his eyes? Open his eyes?

581
00:24:34,057 --> 00:24:36,018
How dare you
let the Fourth Prince open his eyes?

582
00:24:36,057 --> 00:24:37,297
Who do you think you are?

583
00:24:37,898 --> 00:24:39,738
Wasn't it you who told me
to show off more?

584
00:24:39,777 --> 00:24:40,738
- Show off?
- Your Highness!

585
00:24:40,777 --> 00:24:42,097
- Calm down.
- I won't show off then.

586
00:24:42,097 --> 00:24:43,258
Forget it.

587
00:24:43,617 --> 00:24:46,097
The Fourth Prince is the apple
of the Empress Dowager's eye.

588
00:24:46,097 --> 00:24:48,337
He has never left her since childhood.

589
00:24:48,498 --> 00:24:49,658
How dare you

590
00:24:49,978 --> 00:24:51,938
instigate him to go out and play?

591
00:24:52,057 --> 00:24:53,337
What if something goes wrong?

592
00:24:53,377 --> 00:24:54,738
Can you take responsibility?

593
00:24:54,777 --> 00:24:57,297
Father, it was the Fourth Prince
who suggested it to me.

594
00:24:57,297 --> 00:24:58,097
Nonsense!

595
00:24:58,178 --> 00:24:59,178
Even if he wanted to go out,

596
00:24:59,178 --> 00:25:00,658
he wouldn't ask
a waste like you for help.

597
00:25:05,377 --> 00:25:07,337
What? You want to argue?

598
00:25:08,178 --> 00:25:08,777
No, I don't.

599
00:25:08,777 --> 00:25:10,418
Then hold it back.

600
00:25:10,498 --> 00:25:12,057
You look like a pillar.

601
00:25:12,857 --> 00:25:14,137
I don't know who you take after.

602
00:25:16,777 --> 00:25:17,418
I...

603
00:25:23,057 --> 00:25:23,777
Master,

604
00:25:24,377 --> 00:25:26,577
do you really want
to place this ginseng here?

605
00:25:26,777 --> 00:25:27,857
Isn't it strange?

606
00:25:28,857 --> 00:25:29,658
We're newly opened.

607
00:25:29,817 --> 00:25:30,337
The prestige

608
00:25:30,377 --> 00:25:30,898
and facade

609
00:25:31,097 --> 00:25:31,857
all depend on it.

610
00:25:32,458 --> 00:25:33,738
It's a hundred-year ginseng.

611
00:25:33,777 --> 00:25:34,617
Its spirit

612
00:25:34,658 --> 00:25:36,057
will last forever.

613
00:25:37,577 --> 00:25:38,658
What are you writing?

614
00:25:45,057 --> 00:25:46,337
Big discount for the opening

615
00:25:46,418 --> 00:25:47,498
of Jiren Pharmacy.

616
00:25:47,658 --> 00:25:48,297
Treat two patients

617
00:25:48,297 --> 00:25:49,057
for the price of one.

618
00:25:49,057 --> 00:25:49,738
Full refund

619
00:25:49,857 --> 00:25:50,458
if not cured.

620
00:25:51,658 --> 00:25:52,738
Why are you doing this too?

621
00:25:54,857 --> 00:25:56,178
We have been open for days.

622
00:25:56,258 --> 00:25:57,817
Not a single customer has come.

623
00:25:58,178 --> 00:25:59,658
When I was soliciting customers,

624
00:25:59,658 --> 00:26:00,658
I saw other shops

625
00:26:00,658 --> 00:26:01,698
promoting like this.

626
00:26:01,777 --> 00:26:02,377
The effect

627
00:26:02,658 --> 00:26:03,458
was quite good.

628
00:26:03,577 --> 00:26:04,658
Soliciting customers?

629
00:26:04,857 --> 00:26:07,057
The words you use
are really embarrassing.

630
00:26:07,377 --> 00:26:08,938
It's the journey that makes the monk.

631
00:26:09,577 --> 00:26:11,018
This is our family's
only source of income.

632
00:26:11,018 --> 00:26:12,577
We all rely on this pharmacy.

633
00:26:12,857 --> 00:26:13,658
Master,

634
00:26:14,458 --> 00:26:16,218
you are a doctor.

635
00:26:16,297 --> 00:26:18,057
You are meant to save lives.

636
00:26:18,297 --> 00:26:20,057
People will come
if they are sick, right?

637
00:26:20,218 --> 00:26:22,057
What's "Treat two patients
for the price of one"?

638
00:26:22,458 --> 00:26:24,057
Did you forget
what you taught me before?

639
00:26:24,178 --> 00:26:25,698
We only want to save lives

640
00:26:25,698 --> 00:26:27,218
without caring if the medicine is sold.

641
00:26:30,258 --> 00:26:30,817
You remember it.

642
00:26:35,377 --> 00:26:36,458
Treating patients

643
00:26:36,577 --> 00:26:37,817
and making a living do not contradict

644
00:26:39,097 --> 00:26:39,698
each other,

645
00:26:40,498 --> 00:26:41,137
right?

646
00:26:44,898 --> 00:26:45,978
You've lost your dream.

647
00:27:00,058 --> 00:27:02,778
(Jiren Pharmacy)

648
00:27:02,898 --> 00:27:03,777
Young Lord,

649
00:27:03,777 --> 00:27:05,658
I'm sorry
for letting you down this time.

650
00:27:05,698 --> 00:27:08,337
(Spring River Restaurant)
I will make up to you next time.

651
00:27:08,498 --> 00:27:08,817
Get lost.

652
00:27:08,857 --> 00:27:10,018
Young Lord, please calm down.

653
00:27:10,617 --> 00:27:11,498
Get lost now.

654
00:27:12,218 --> 00:27:14,978
I... Mantis Fist!
Tiger-Crane Double Form!

655
00:27:15,178 --> 00:27:16,617
- I will scare you to death.
- Young Lord.

656
00:27:18,178 --> 00:27:19,658
What kind of people are these?

657
00:27:21,377 --> 00:27:22,817
And it's so hot today.

658
00:27:29,777 --> 00:27:30,817
What are you doing?

659
00:27:34,698 --> 00:27:35,857
You shouted at me?

660
00:27:36,090 --> 00:27:37,728
(Fortune Telling)

661
00:27:38,178 --> 00:27:39,337
You misunderstood.

662
00:27:39,377 --> 00:27:40,978
I was not shouting at you.

663
00:27:40,978 --> 00:27:41,777
I was...

664
00:27:42,297 --> 00:27:43,658
I was shouting at him.

665
00:27:44,377 --> 00:27:45,057
Him?

666
00:27:45,978 --> 00:27:48,498
But your shouting just now scared me.

667
00:27:48,898 --> 00:27:49,898
I'm sorry, Childe.

668
00:27:49,978 --> 00:27:51,178
I won't shout anymore.

669
00:27:51,418 --> 00:27:52,137
Sorry.

670
00:27:53,978 --> 00:27:54,898
What are all these for?

671
00:27:56,498 --> 00:27:57,617
To make a living.

672
00:27:58,258 --> 00:27:58,817
Fine.

673
00:27:59,978 --> 00:28:02,272
I want you to give me a fortune telling.

674
00:28:04,458 --> 00:28:05,337
Okay.

675
00:28:05,777 --> 00:28:07,857
Just by looking at your appearance,

676
00:28:08,258 --> 00:28:09,938
I know you are from a noble family.

677
00:28:09,978 --> 00:28:11,137
You are rich and noble.

678
00:28:13,297 --> 00:28:13,898
Go on.

679
00:28:14,258 --> 00:28:16,498
Your appearance tells me

680
00:28:17,978 --> 00:28:19,698
you have the help of a noble person.

681
00:28:19,698 --> 00:28:22,218
You are in purple today.

682
00:28:22,577 --> 00:28:25,898
You have a purple glow on your face
and a purple aura around you.

683
00:28:25,898 --> 00:28:27,817
You must be

684
00:28:27,817 --> 00:28:29,978
doing well recently.

685
00:28:30,018 --> 00:28:31,698
You have very good luck.

686
00:28:34,777 --> 00:28:36,498
Good luck. Good luck.

687
00:28:36,498 --> 00:28:37,218
Yes, yes.

688
00:28:37,258 --> 00:28:39,418
You are indeed brilliant.

689
00:28:39,418 --> 00:28:40,337
Thank you.

690
00:28:41,057 --> 00:28:41,738
Did you foresee

691
00:28:41,777 --> 00:28:43,057
that you would be beaten today?

692
00:28:44,857 --> 00:28:47,537
Good luck, huh?

693
00:28:47,674 --> 00:28:48,577
(Kindness Brings Good Luck)

694
00:28:48,577 --> 00:28:49,577
Good luck?

695
00:28:51,178 --> 00:28:53,377
Young Lord, where have you been?

696
00:28:53,377 --> 00:28:55,018
I just went for a stroll.
What's the problem?

697
00:28:55,297 --> 00:28:56,698
His Highness has been waiting for you.

698
00:28:56,698 --> 00:28:58,297
You really made a scene this time.

699
00:28:58,377 --> 00:28:59,218
He's waiting for me?

700
00:28:59,777 --> 00:29:00,777
Quickly! Quickly!

701
00:29:00,777 --> 00:29:01,577
Hurry!

702
00:29:03,178 --> 00:29:04,898
By His Majesty's decree,

703
00:29:04,978 --> 00:29:08,297
"Lord Ling, your family
has been dedicated for generations.

704
00:29:08,297 --> 00:29:09,698
You are loyal,

705
00:29:09,698 --> 00:29:11,817
and you're the pillars of our dynasty.

706
00:29:11,817 --> 00:29:13,577
You're deeply trusted by me.

707
00:29:13,617 --> 00:29:15,577
The Fourth Prince is young and ignorant.

708
00:29:15,577 --> 00:29:18,418
I specially instruct the Fourth Prince
to go out of the palace for experience,

709
00:29:18,458 --> 00:29:20,377
observe the various aspects
of people's lives,

710
00:29:20,418 --> 00:29:22,898
and understand the right path
to do good to the society.

711
00:29:22,978 --> 00:29:26,018
During his time outside the palace,
he will stay in your mansion.

712
00:29:26,018 --> 00:29:29,258
I hope that your family
will take good care of him

713
00:29:29,297 --> 00:29:31,857
to alleviate my worries."

714
00:29:32,577 --> 00:29:34,097
That's all.

715
00:29:34,377 --> 00:29:36,777
Yes, Your Majesty.

716
00:29:43,777 --> 00:29:44,297
Allow me.

717
00:29:45,498 --> 00:29:46,297
Your Highness,

718
00:29:46,498 --> 00:29:47,537
congratulations.

719
00:29:47,577 --> 00:29:49,057
Thank you, Eunuch Wang.

720
00:29:49,698 --> 00:29:53,258
But I wonder
what His Majesty's intention is.

721
00:29:54,777 --> 00:29:58,057
I wonder what the Young Lord said
to the Fourth Prince.

722
00:29:58,057 --> 00:30:00,258
The Fourth Prince
didn't demand much since he was little.

723
00:30:00,297 --> 00:30:01,577
He suddenly petitioned His Majesty,

724
00:30:01,617 --> 00:30:03,258
saying he wanted to go out
for some experience.

725
00:30:03,258 --> 00:30:05,577
But His Majesty agreed immediately.

726
00:30:07,658 --> 00:30:10,617
But Her Majesty, the Empress Dowager...

727
00:30:10,658 --> 00:30:13,258
Don't worry. His Majesty has decided.

728
00:30:13,258 --> 00:30:15,458
Her Majesty won't object to that.

729
00:30:15,898 --> 00:30:16,658
Your Highness,

730
00:30:17,018 --> 00:30:19,137
this is a rare opportunity.

731
00:30:19,258 --> 00:30:20,498
I understand.

732
00:30:20,577 --> 00:30:22,018
Thank you, Eunuch Wang.

733
00:30:24,186 --> 00:30:27,107
There's something I must remind you of.

734
00:30:27,746 --> 00:30:30,107
You must ensure the safety
of the Fourth Prince.

735
00:30:30,147 --> 00:30:31,907
If anything goes wrong,

736
00:30:31,907 --> 00:30:34,587
Her Majesty will definitely blame you.

737
00:30:34,867 --> 00:30:36,867
Thank you for the reminder, Eunuch Wang.

738
00:30:37,107 --> 00:30:38,387
I have matters to attend to.

739
00:30:38,466 --> 00:30:39,706
I'm leaving now.

740
00:30:39,986 --> 00:30:41,186
Please wait.

741
00:30:41,787 --> 00:30:42,666
Eunuch Wang.

742
00:30:43,547 --> 00:30:44,827
This is a small token of appreciation.

743
00:30:44,867 --> 00:30:46,107
- This is unnecessary.
- Just take it.

744
00:30:46,107 --> 00:30:47,147
- It's okay.
- Your Highness.

745
00:30:47,186 --> 00:30:48,627
- You don't have to.
- Just take it.

746
00:30:48,666 --> 00:30:50,946
- You don't have to.
- Just take it.

747
00:30:56,266 --> 00:30:56,867
Father.

748
00:31:02,587 --> 00:31:03,706
Be gentle.

749
00:31:15,362 --> 00:31:16,307
(Lord Ling's Mansion)

750
00:31:16,307 --> 00:31:17,587
(Lord Ling's Mansion)
Spare me, sir.

751
00:31:18,746 --> 00:31:20,426
Young Lord, he's here.

752
00:31:22,587 --> 00:31:23,986
What are you doing?

753
00:31:23,986 --> 00:31:25,347
Can't you do things properly?

754
00:31:25,347 --> 00:31:26,387
I asked you to invite him here.

755
00:31:26,466 --> 00:31:27,547
Who told you to catch him?

756
00:31:27,547 --> 00:31:28,067
Leave us.

757
00:31:29,266 --> 00:31:30,666
Master, please rise.

758
00:31:30,666 --> 00:31:31,147
Come.

759
00:31:31,186 --> 00:31:31,587
I…

760
00:31:31,666 --> 00:31:32,587
Here.

761
00:31:33,787 --> 00:31:36,147
I presume you must have guessed

762
00:31:36,266 --> 00:31:37,627
who I am.

763
00:31:39,946 --> 00:31:40,946
Young Lord.

764
00:31:41,506 --> 00:31:43,907
You are indeed wise.

765
00:31:46,186 --> 00:31:47,506
What are you doing? Leave us.

766
00:31:47,547 --> 00:31:48,387
Yes.

767
00:31:50,746 --> 00:31:53,627
Today, I was indeed too impulsive.

768
00:31:53,666 --> 00:31:56,506
But your calculation is really accurate.

769
00:31:57,867 --> 00:31:58,587
Accurate?

770
00:31:58,946 --> 00:31:59,787
Did you forget you said

771
00:31:59,986 --> 00:32:01,307
I would have a noble person's help?

772
00:32:02,347 --> 00:32:03,506
Yes, a noble person.

773
00:32:03,506 --> 00:32:05,347
Master, to be honest,

774
00:32:05,387 --> 00:32:07,266
there is indeed a noble person
coming to our mansion.

775
00:32:07,307 --> 00:32:09,266
I wonder if you can
give me some pointers

776
00:32:09,307 --> 00:32:12,307
on how to win over this noble person.

777
00:32:14,107 --> 00:32:15,307
About the matter...

778
00:32:15,466 --> 00:32:19,067
As they say, man proposes, God disposes.

779
00:32:19,986 --> 00:32:22,426
This needs a long-term plan.

780
00:32:23,347 --> 00:32:24,067
Professional!

781
00:32:24,307 --> 00:32:25,627
You are indeed a master.

782
00:32:26,266 --> 00:32:28,426
By the way,
I still don't know your name.

783
00:32:28,787 --> 00:32:30,266
My name is Li Tengyun.

784
00:32:30,266 --> 00:32:31,107
Good.

785
00:32:31,666 --> 00:32:32,466
Master Li,

786
00:32:32,666 --> 00:32:34,986
are you interested in
hanging out with me?

787
00:32:35,746 --> 00:32:36,387
Hanging out?

788
00:32:37,587 --> 00:32:38,666
I mean, assisting me.

789
00:32:40,307 --> 00:32:41,506
You can foresee things,

790
00:32:41,506 --> 00:32:42,867
and I have a high position and power.

791
00:32:42,907 --> 00:32:45,307
We are simply a heaven-made match.

792
00:32:45,946 --> 00:32:47,067
A heaven-made match?

793
00:32:47,387 --> 00:32:48,026
Yes.

794
00:32:48,466 --> 00:32:49,426
Starting today,

795
00:32:49,466 --> 00:32:52,627
