deal with the Fourth Prince.

796
00:32:53,746 --> 00:32:56,387
The Fourth... Prince?

797
00:32:56,867 --> 00:32:57,547
Master,

798
00:32:58,107 --> 00:32:59,907
as long as you help me rise to the top,

799
00:32:59,946 --> 00:33:02,426
I can make you benefit from it too.

800
00:33:35,067 --> 00:33:37,666
(On the day of Gengyou,
the weather is clear.)

801
00:33:37,787 --> 00:33:41,216
(I didn't expect that I, Li Tengyun,
would also have my day.)

802
00:33:50,907 --> 00:33:52,147
Did you soak your feet?

803
00:33:52,186 --> 00:33:53,226
Yes.

804
00:33:53,266 --> 00:33:54,746
Soaking your feet before bed
is comfortable.

805
00:33:55,067 --> 00:33:56,186
It's quite comfortable.

806
00:34:07,322 --> 00:34:08,442
I heard

807
00:34:09,642 --> 00:34:11,681
you are a renowned doctor in Qing City.

808
00:34:12,002 --> 00:34:12,881
I'm flattered.

809
00:34:13,361 --> 00:34:14,482
Then why do you

810
00:34:14,522 --> 00:34:16,082
prefer to pay 20 taels each month

811
00:34:16,241 --> 00:34:17,562
to stay here?

812
00:34:20,506 --> 00:34:21,347
Young man,

813
00:34:21,347 --> 00:34:22,986
I heard you are a servant here,

814
00:34:23,026 --> 00:34:24,347
and you don't take any money.

815
00:34:24,907 --> 00:34:25,986
I think you are

816
00:34:25,986 --> 00:34:28,387
young, promising, and robust.

817
00:34:28,907 --> 00:34:30,506
Why are you doing this?

818
00:34:31,307 --> 00:34:32,146
Because I...

819
00:34:35,506 --> 00:34:36,066
Let's sleep.

820
00:34:36,307 --> 00:34:37,506
Just sleep, Master.

821
00:34:37,626 --> 00:34:39,227
Right, it's getting late.

